annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L18; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S8; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: translational elongation; translation; neurogenesis; maturation of SSU-rRNA from tricistronic rRNA transcript (SSU-rRNA, 5.8S rRNA, LSU-rRNA); Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eS8 family
